## ğŸ” Security

### Firebase Security Rules

The platform uses Firebase Security Rules to protect user data:

- Users can only read/write their own profile and progress
- Teachers can create classes and manage their own classes
- Students can join classes and view class information
- All operations require authentication

For the full security rules configuration, see [DEPLOYMENT-CHECKLIST.md](DEPLOYMENT-CHECKLIST.md#firestore-security-rules)

